  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study investigate the impact of comprehensive geriatric assessments using activity of
      daily living (ADL), instrumental activity of daily living (IADL), and Charlson's comorbidity
      index (CCI) on survival and toxicities in Korean patients with diffuse large B-cell lymphoma
      (DLBCL) treated with R-CHOP.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
