    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with newly diagnosed CD20+ DLBCL

          -  65 years old or over

          -  Scheduled to receive R-CHOP chemotherapy

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Other histology than CD20+ DLBCL

          -  Primary central nervous system DLBCL

          -  Patients with a diagnosis of cancer (other than basal or squamous cell carcinoma of
             the skin, cervical carcinoma in situ, well differentiated thyroid cancer [papillary or
             follicular thyroid cancer]) within 3 years before the study entry or with any
             treatment for cancer within 3 years before entry

          -  Consent withdrawal
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
